Name: system_info
Description: System information utilities.
Version: 1.0

Commands:
- system_info
  Get OS/CPU/memory/disk/GPU info.
  Parameters:
  - include_disks (boolean, optional)
  - include_network (boolean, optional)
  - include_users (boolean, optional)
  - include_env (boolean, optional)
  - include_battery (boolean, optional)
